The pickups have been upgraded with some nice hot Dragonfire Invader style ceramic single coils with chrome pickup covers,and the guitar has been wired for tone control on all three pickups.The bridge and neck pickups both work with the neck pickups tone control. The capacitor has been upgraded with a .033uf axial capacitor . More range of tone control and a smoother response. I added the black pickguard,rear tremolo cover, pickup covers,switch tip and whammy bar tip to get the vibe I was going for. This guitar sounds really good,plays good and it looks super cool.
